desc_content.paragraph:
Creates a CourseTeamMembership entry - i.e: a relationship between a user and a team.
                                user_row is a dictionary where key is column name and value is the row value.
                                {‘mode’: ‘ masters’,’topic_0’: ‘’,’topic_1’: ‘team 2’,’topic_2’: None,’user_model’: <user_obj>}

list_item.paragraph:
order_by: Orders the results. Currently only ‘name’ and ‘team_count’ are supported;
                                    the default value is ‘name’. If ‘team_count’ is specified, topics are returned first sorted
                                    by number of teams per topic (descending), with a secondary sort of ‘name’.
